#

Spicy Turkey Lettuce Wraps

$12.5
350 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow CalorieGluten-FreePaleo

Tags:

Protein-PackedHealthyFreshWraps

Description

Savory turkey filling wrapped in crisp lettuce leaves for a fresh, low-calorie delight.

Ingredients

  • Ground Turkey: 1 lb
  • Green Bell Pepper: 1, diced
  • Red Onion: 1/2, diced
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Soy Sauce (or Coconut Aminos): 2 tbsp
  • Sriracha Sauce: 1 tbsp
  • Lettuce Leaves: 8 large leaves
  • Olive Oil: 1 tbsp
  • Green Onions: 2, chopped
  • Sesame Seeds: 1 tbsp
